summary:
I still can’t fully process that all of this actually happened. 
Us from all latam countries never have a chance of meeting our...
body:
I still can’t fully process that all of this actually happened.

Us from all latam countries never have a chance of meeting our faves, is just how things are I guess, that’s why I’m so happy Dan and Phil actually could come to visit us.

Thanks @danielhowell and @amazingphil for the kind words and for making that day so special to all of us who were there.

And thank you so much to Lola @dnpsuck and Vero @octolevi. All their help was what made all this magical adventure a reality. I really hope we can meet again some day 💕.
